source.name: IDOR FY 2011 Lottery Sales by Zip Code
source.description: Sales report SLS989-01 reflects all Lottery sales for fiscal year 2011 (current). The games are Instant, Pic 3, Pic 4, Subscription, Mega, Lotto, Little Lotto, Powerball, Pick-n-Play and Raffle.
